<plot>Ravi Verma is an honest and dedicated police officer, who has been assigned to lead the bodyguard team of the State's Chief Minister, Sevak Ram. Ravi's younger brother, Raghuveer, a college student, is also honest and dedicated and will not tolerate any injustice being done to anyone. In so doing, Raghuveer, himself is arrested and imprisoned on false charges. Ravi is enraged at Raghuveer at his embarassment, and will have nothing to do with him anymore. Raghuveer is released, and soon he and his friends acquire a reputation, bringing them into direct confrontation with Nitiram Chanakya, his brother, Ganpat, and Chief Minister Sevak Ram himself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?453751</url></doc>
